15 earned their well-deserved reputation for high standards of athletic achievement, the quality
16 of their play, and the stiff competition they presented to their opponents; and
17 WHEREAS, this accomplished team achieved a remarkable 32-10 record and represented
18 Lanier County with pride and determination.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
20 congratulate the Lanier County High School baseball team on its victory at the GHSA Class
21 A Division II State Baseball Championship and extend best wishes for continued success.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
23 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Lanier County
24 High School baseball team.
